#

Zucchini Noodles with Avocado Pesto

10 min
$10
350 kcal
Difficulty: 20%
Servings: 2

Allergens:

Nuts

Dietary Tags:

VeganGluten-FreeLow-Carb

Cuisine:

American

Course:

Main

Tags:

QuickHealthyVegetarian

Description

A fresh and creamy dish that combines the lightness of zucchini noodles with a rich avocado pesto, perfect for a healthy meal without the fuss.

Ingredients

  • zucchini: 2 medium
  • avocado: 1 ripe
  • fresh basil leaves: 1 cup
  • garlic: 1 clove
  • lemon juice: 2 tablespoons
  • pine nuts: 1/4 cup
  • olive oil: 2 tablespoons
  • salt: to taste
  • pepper: to taste
